scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AGKA9MZaeos8lqfW7_Z3gsX&oh=00_AYBHoVFQBIPgQgJFWerJTI9QWY-cPoRcDVubTWbygyp8jQ&oe=66D9A9DE"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "cover.png", "id": "1819228061920273", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982452_1819228065253606_407037206585227872_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1k_syI3D3BkQ7kNvgE_Oi34&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AGKA9MZaeos8lqfW7_Z3gsX&oh=00_AYCdZSnyls-fa7Hxp7OXKIhp9fV4CTtGhCo8OYS8tshVVw&oe=66D9870A"}, "display_name": "Pinfall", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Pinfall: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Pinfall,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters the realm of immersive virtual reality. Prepare to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Pinfall\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport.\nGame Overview\n\n\"Pinfall\" is a cutting-edge VR game that redefines the bowling experience by placing players in a vibrant cosmic arena. The game challenges your precision, skill, and timing as you aim to score points by knocking down pins in various celestial-themed lanes. Each game session offers a unique adventure, filled with stunning visuals and dynamic gameplay.", "short_description": "Pinfall: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Pinfall,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters the realm of immersive virtual reality. Prepare to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Pinfall\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/pinfall/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_servi